        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Andriy Skulysh",
          "email": "Andriy_Skulysh@xyratex.com",
          "date": "2014-04-02 10:57:07.000000000",
          "tz": 180
        },
        "subject": "LU-4852 osc: osc_extent_truncate()) ASSERTION( !ext->oe_urgent ) failed",
        "message": "LU-4852 osc: osc_extent_truncate()) ASSERTION( !ext->oe_urgent ) failed\n\nThe bug was caused by race between truncate & fsync.\nosc_extent_wait() doesn't takes into account oe_trunc_pending\nduring setting oe_urgent. The race arises after\nosc_object_unlock().\nosc_extent_wait() should ignore extents with oe_trunc_pending\nwhile waiting for OES_INV. osc_cache_truncate_end() will set\noe_urgent and call osc_io_unplug_async()\n\nChange-Id: I3c8ba73e3abb7de31326efe5221321d79b80aa5a\nXyratex-bug-id: LELUS-239\nSigned-off-by: Andriy Skulysh <Andriy_Skulysh@xyratex.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
